{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/jekyll/change-korean-font/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"JIKOID","description":"천천히 그리고 꾸준히"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9180501d-4af2-5283-bf6c-f3e4cf4750a1","excerpt":"이번에는 Github 블로그에 한글 폰트를 적용해보려고 한다. 구글 웹 폰트 import 하기 먼저 구글에서 사용할 font 를 찾아서 improt 해야 한다. 아래의 사이트에서 폰트를 검색할 수 있다. https://fonts.google.com/?subset=korean&noto…","html":"<p>이번에는 Github 블로그에 한글 폰트를 적용해보려고 한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"구글-웹-폰트-import-하기\">구글 웹 폰트 import 하기</h2>\n<p>먼저 구글에서 사용할 font 를 찾아서 improt 해야 한다.<br>\n아래의 사이트에서 폰트를 검색할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://fonts.google.com/?subset=korean&#x26;noto.script=Kore\">https://fonts.google.com/?subset=korean&#x26;noto.script=Kore</a></p>\n<p>원하는 폰트를 위의 사이트에서 검색하고나서 클릭해서 상세 정보를 확인해보면 아래의 사진과 같이 상단에 <code class=\"language-text\">Get font</code> 가 보인다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/764d7/image.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 24%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/0a47e/image.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/8a4e8/image.png 150w,\n/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/5a46d/image.png 300w,\n/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/0a47e/image.png 600w,\n/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/1cfc2/image.png 900w,\n/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/c1b63/image.png 1200w,\n/static/cf35a1cdc0cf0a1caf4974e1a0563047/764d7/image.png 1782w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Get font</code> 를 클릭해서 들어가면 아래와 같이 나오게 되는데 <code class=\"language-text\">Get embed code</code> 를 누른다.</p>\n<br>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/764d7/image2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/0a47e/image2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/8a4e8/image2.png 150w,\n/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/5a46d/image2.png 300w,\n/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/0a47e/image2.png 600w,\n/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/1cfc2/image2.png 900w,\n/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/c1b63/image2.png 1200w,\n/static/c1f235e0e76c6ca85689ddc2d48806d2/764d7/image2.png 1782w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>다음으로 Web Tab 에서 <code class=\"language-text\">Web</code> 과 <code class=\"language-text\">@import</code> 선택을 할 수 있는데 <code class=\"language-text\">@import</code> 를 선택한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/019a6/image3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 59.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/0a47e/image3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/8a4e8/image3.png 150w,\n/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/5a46d/image3.png 300w,\n/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/0a47e/image3.png 600w,\n/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/1cfc2/image3.png 900w,\n/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/c1b63/image3.png 1200w,\n/static/025328a0b05f680a76e9a1a0ea3ae231/019a6/image3.png 1818w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<p>그럼 <code class=\"language-text\">@import</code> 할 수 있는 코드를 제공해주는데 해당 코드를 복사한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nanum+Gothic&amp;display=swap');</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<p>이렇게 복사한 코드를 <code class=\"language-text\">assets/css/main.scss</code> 파일에 복사해준다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\">---\n# Only the main Sass file needs front matter (the dashes are enough)\nsearch: false\n---\n\n@charset \"utf-8\";\n\n@import \"minimal-mistakes/skins/{{ site.minimal_mistakes_skin | default: 'default' }}\"; // skin\n@import \"minimal-mistakes\"; // main partials\n\n// Font 변경\n@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nanum+Gothic&amp;display=swap');</code></pre></div>\n<p>마지막으로 블로그의 font 가 변경되었는지 확인한다.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Github 블로그 한글 폰트 적용하기 (Minimal Mistakes)","date":"2024년 05월 15일","description":"Github Jekyll 블로그에서 한글 폰트를 적용하는 방법입니다.","tags":["github","minimal_mistakes"],"categories":"blog/jekyll"},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EA%B8%80-%EC%9B%B9-%ED%8F%B0%ED%8A%B8-import-%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\">구글 웹 폰트 import 하기</a></li>\n</ul>","timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/jekyll/change-korean-font/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/jekyll/change-font-size/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Github 블로그 폰트 사이즈 변경하기 (Minimal Mistakes)","categories":"blog/jekyll"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["1128308798","2390591302","4172325373"],"slicesMap":{}}